sequenceDiagram
    participant Page as config.js render()
    participant Bus as PanelStateBus
    participant Sidebar as config-sidebar.js
    participant Groups as config-groups.js
    participant DOM as Browser DOM

    Page->>Bus: new PanelStateBus()
    Page->>Bus: register(44 panels)
    Page->>Page: init all *Values + setLoading states
    Page->>DOM: draw() → 渲染 hero + 搜索框 + 两栏布局
    Page->>Sidebar: renderSidebar(CONFIG_GROUPS)
    Sidebar-->>DOM: 侧栏 nav 列表 (9 个分组链接)
    Page->>DOM: 按 CONFIG_GROUPS 循环渲染分组 section
    Note over Page,DOM: 每个 section: id="cfg-group-{id}"<br/>内含分组标题 + panel 列表
    
    Page->>Page: 绑定 IntersectionObserver
    Note over Page,DOM: 每个 section 进入视口<br/>→ 侧栏对应链接 .active

    Page->>Page: load() → 顺序加载 44 个配置
    loop 每个面板
        Page->>API: hermesXxxConfigRead()
        Page->>Bus: setLoading(id, false)
        Page->>Page: draw() 局部刷新
    end

    opt 用户搜索
        DOM->>Sidebar: input 事件触发 filterPanels(query)
        Sidebar->>DOM: 遍历 .hm-panel → display:none 不匹配项
        Sidebar->>DOM: 隐藏空分组 section 标题
    end

    opt 用户点击侧栏链接
        Sidebar->>DOM: document.getElementById('cfg-group-xxx')
        DOM->>DOM: scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })
    end
